race.description: Black Caviar Lightning Race Day, 14 Feb Handicap
race.comment: YES I KNOW (14) is looking to turn the tables on FIORENOT (2) from their clash here on New Year's Eve over this trip and sets up well to do so. The pace was strong there and YES I KNOW sat close to it while also covering a bit of extra ground. He meets FIORENOT 2.5kg better off at the weights now and fares far better at the draw. FIORENOT is likely to get right back and that could prove the difference. DARK SIMBA (6) is the danger to that pair. He's been okay without really putting his hand up this time in, but he's been slowly building and now gets to 1800m which should ideally. His SP profile suggests he's better than BM70 grade. AMBASSADORIAL (8) stuck on well behind FIORENOT first up and should only be fitter. He doesn't have the upside of a few but has to be considered. ALL SO CLEAR (3) ran well in a dash home here fresh, he could add some value to the exotics at big odds.
